Jchord - the future of NoSQL :-)

Subassignment: To make a message passing middleware that can join a network topology and exchange messages to peers of interest.

API:
-connectToPeer(PeerInfo)
-disconnectFromPeer(PeerInfo)
-sendMessage(PeerInfo, Message)
-getMessageBuffer()? "Throw" messages instead?

Main Class:
MessagingPeer - A message passing interface used to create connections and send/receive messages to/from peers.
